<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
  <meta charset="UTF-8">
  <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
  <title>Reset Your MinifigsMania Password</title>
  <style>
    * {
      box-sizing: border-box;
    }
    body {
      font-family: Arial, sans-serif;
      line-height: 1.6;
      color: #333;
      margin: 0;
      padding: 0;
      background-color: #f7f7f7;
    }
    .container {
      max-width: 700px;
      margin: 0 auto;
      background: #fff;
      padding: 20px;
      border: 1px solid #e0e0e0;
    }
    .header {
      text-align: center;
      padding: 10px 0;
      border-bottom: 2px solid #6366F1;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .logo {
      height: 100px;
      width: auto;
      border-radius: 4px;
      border: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    .section {
      margin-bottom: 25px;
      padding-bottom: 15px;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    .section-title {
      background-color: #6366F1;
      color: white;
      padding: 8px 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 15px;
      font-size: 16px;
    }
    .order-status {
      background-color: #e7f7e7;
      color: #2e8b57;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
      text-align: center;
      font-size: 18px;
      font-weight: bold;
    }
    .info-row {
      display: flex;
      justify-content: space-between;
      padding: 8px 0;
      border-bottom: 1px solid #f5f5f5;
    }
    .info-label {
      font-weight: 600;
      width: 40%;
    }
    .info-text {
      width: 60%;
      text-align: right;
    }
    .actions {
      text-align: center;
      margin: 25px 0;
    }
    .button {
      display: inline-block;
      background-color: #6366F1;
      color: white;
      padding: 12px 25px;
      text-decoration: none;
      border-radius: 5px;
      font-weight: bold;
      font-size: 16px;
      margin: 0 10px;
    }
    .tag {
      display: inline-block;
      padding: 4px 8px;
      border-radius: 12px;
      font-size: 12px;
      font-weight: bold;
      color: white;
      margin-right: 5px;
    }
    .tag-info {
      background-color: #3B82F6;
    }
    .tag-warning {
      background-color: #F59E0B;
    }
    .tag-danger {
      background-color: #EF4444;
    }
    .footer {
      margin-top: 30px;
      text-align: center;
      padding: 20px;
      font-size: 12px;
      color: #777;
      border-top: 1px solid #eee;
    }
    .alert {
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin-bottom: 20px;
    }
    .alert-info {
      background-color: #EEF2FF;
      border-left: 4px solid #6366F1;
    }
    .alert-warning {
      background-color: #FEF3C7;
      border-left: 4px solid #F59E0B;
    }
    .alert-danger {
      background-color: #FEE2E2;
      border-left: 4px solid #EF4444;
    }
    .security-notice {
      background-color: #f8f8f8;
      padding: 15px;
      border-radius: 5px;
      margin: 20px 0;
      border: 1px solid #eaeaea;
    }
    .security-title {
      font-weight: 600;
      font-size: 14px;
      margin-bottom: 8px;
      color: #333;
    }
    .manual-link {
      word-break: break-all;
      color: #6366F1;
      font-weight: 500;
    }
    .social-links {
      margin: 15px 0;
    }
    .social-icon {
      display: inline-block;
      margin: 0 8px;
    }
    .help-links {
      margin-bottom: 15px;
    }
    .help-link {
      color: #6366F1;
      text-decoration: none;
      margin: 0 10px;
    }
  </style>
</head>
<body>
  <div class="container">
    <div class="header">
      <img class="logo" src="https://res.cloudinary.com/duzlv0fex/image/upload/v1744295709/urhndchpkmqiufym8mbv.png" alt="MinifigsMania">
      <h1>Reset Password</h1>
    </div>

    <div class="order-status">
      Password Reset Request Received
    </div>

    <p>Hello <%= @user.name %>,</p>
    <p>We received a request to reset the password for your MinifigsMania account. Please follow the steps below to securely reset your password.</p>

    <div class="alert alert-info">
      <p><strong>This link will expire in 10 minutes</strong> - Please reset your password as soon as possible.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">Reset Instructions</div>
      <p>Click the button below to create a new password for your account:</p>

      <div class="actions">
        <a href="<%= @reset_url %>" class="button">Reset My Password</a>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="alert alert-warning">
      <p><strong>Did not request this password reset?</strong> If you did not request to reset your password, please contact our support team immediately or secure your account by changing your password.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="section">
      <div class="section-title">Account Details</div>
      <div class="info-row">
        <div class="info-label">Email Address:</div>
        <div class="info-text"><%= @user.email %></div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-row">
        <div class="info-label">Request Time:</div>
        <div class="info-text"><%= Time.now.strftime('%B %d, %Y at %I:%M %p') %></div>
      </div>
      <div class="info-row">
        <div class="info-label">Valid for:</div>
        <div class="info-text">10 minutes</div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <div class="security-notice">
      <div class="security-title">ðŸ”’ Security Tips</div>
      <ul>
        <li>Choose a strong password that's at least 8 characters long</li>
        <li>Include uppercase letters, lowercase letters, numbers, and symbols</li>
        <li>Don't reuse passwords from other websites</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <div class="alert alert-danger">
      <p><strong>Never share your password with anyone</strong> - MinifigsMania will never ask for your password via email, phone, or chat.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="footer">
      <div class="social-links">
        <a href="#" class="social-icon">
          <img src="https://img.icons8.com/ios-filled/50/6366F1/facebook-new.png" width="24" alt="Facebook">
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="social-icon">
          <img src="https://img.icons8.com/ios-filled/50/6366F1/instagram-new.png" width="24" alt="Instagram">
        </a>
        <a href="#" class="social-icon">
          <img src="https://img.icons8.com/ios-filled/50/6366F1/twitter.png" width="24" alt="Twitter">
        </a>
      </div>
      
      <div class="help-links">
        <a href="#" class="help-link">Help Center</a>
        <a href="#" class="help-link">Contact Us</a>
        <a href="#" class="help-link">Privacy Policy</a>
      </div>
      
      <p>This is an automated notification from your MinifigsMania store.</p>
      <p>Â© <%= Date.today.year %> MinifigsMania. All rights reserved.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</body>
</html>